{"tid":2274393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四年了","createTime":"2020-11-06T11:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T08:55:49.000Z","uid":250291,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0cfdb7dea1083b838ee4db1b99c572a2c28ee4","tid":2274393,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/east_LYLz5_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Feast_LYLz5_1200x0.png&h=2f8bc35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/walk_SqeIW_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwalk_SqeIW_1200x0.png&h=9cf0b712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chase_Dw7ic_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchase_Dw7ic_1200x0.png&h=d4aba8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161106/photo/bkn-20161106225220064-1106_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161107025746\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161106225220064-1106_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161107025746&h=258d77d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【我們都是這樣走過來的】<br />\n當年今日，魚革之後，宣誓風波，人大釋法。<br />\n13000人，上街。<br />\n本土派帶領遊行隊伍圍堵中聯辦，人潮之多，將德輔道西完全堵塞。<br />\n警民對峙。速龍。垃圾桶陣。遮陣。<br />\nDQ激起千重浪。<br />\n香港人繼普選落閘後再次見識共黨魔爪。<br />\n我地想起義。<br />\n「香港獨立」呼聲響徹西環。<br />\n當日播種，今日萌芽。<br />\n從此香港人明白了：我地要繼續打一場未完嘅仗。<br />\n我地要勝過支配我地嘅禽獸。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族 莊敬自強🏴<br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/igsavehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Figsavehk&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9rktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=71d273c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/igsavehk</a><br />\nIG page: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/_standwithhkers_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2F_standwithhkers_&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9rktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=5f203fd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/_standwithhkers_</a><br />\nFB page: <a href=\"http://fb.com/hkersresist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fhkersresist&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9rktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=62c2336b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/hkersresist</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fdsa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123839462_2689845554663569_1923115681944764648_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=9267fe&amp;_nc_ohc=qoBxrtcmGwkAX_FvD1J&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fdsa1-1.fna&amp;oh=3fe8e350bb659f98059edda66c993a3b&amp;oe=5FCA8F54\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fdsa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F123839462_2689845554663569_1923115681944764648_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D9267fe%26_nc_ohc%3DqoBxrtcmGwkAX_FvD1J%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fdsa1-1.fna%26oh%3D3fe8e350bb659f98059edda66c993a3b%26oe%3D5FCA8F54&h=a2dc6eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aabf061a40545134a44ea9003cc3295e071da8ab","tid":2274393,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78516a27aa336d69f44ea4433766a7d67daecc3","tid":2274393,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbf92ff3fa5f6c00500c926d63d9195b0d85e8d","tid":2274393,"uid":250291,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"仲有當年經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/LSoqyFVnr69y7UFUa3SUEqIrAUgt3gqetDYgNfJyPgEf_OLB58KRwWafeUh6Lj6aHA9rumHsrqc6--YbyoIIsN0P0biQ\"